org.aksw.rex.examplegenerator

Interface ExampleGenerator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleExampleGenerator, UniformDistributionGenerator

    public interface ExampleGenerator
    This class generates examples, i.e., subject object pairs for a given predicate, for generating XPaths.
    Author:
    r.usbeck
